text: "Barracuda" is a song by American rock band Heart released in 1977 on their third studio album Little Queen (1977). The song was included on the live album Live in Atlantic City (2019). ==Track listing== # "Barracuda" - 4:20 ;Live version # "Barracuda (featuring Jerry Cantrell, Dave Navarro, Duff McKagan, Rufus Wainwright, Gretchen Wilson and Carrie Underwood)" - 6:14 ==References== Category:1977 songs Category:Heart (band) songs Category:Diss tracks
